Package: ccs
Version: 2.0.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: bash (>= 4.0), tmux (>= 3.0), cron
Recommends: claude-code
Maintainer: Robin <robin@nurrobin.de>
Homepage: https://github.com/NurRobin/ccs
Description: Claude Code Session manager
 Manages Claude Code sessions inside dedicated tmux sessions with
 descriptions, fuzzy attach, scheduled cron jobs, and sensible tmux
 defaults. Sessions run on an isolated tmux socket.
